trans-unit.source: Contains the classes used to instrument your application.
trans-unit.target: Contém as classes usadas para instrumentar seu aplicativo.

trans-unit.source: The instrumentation, when enabled, logs the event data to the Event Tracing for Windows (ETW) tracing subsystem.
trans-unit.target: A instrumentação, quando habilitada, registra em log os dados de evento no subsistema de rastreamento ETW (Rastreamento de Eventos para Windows).

trans-unit.source: For a complete description of ETW, see <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows-hardware/drivers/devtest/event-tracing-for-windows--etw-">Event Tracing for Windows</see>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter uma descrição completa do ETW, consulte <see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows-hardware/drivers/devtest/event-tracing-for-windows--etw-">Event Tracing for Windows</see> (Rastreamento de Eventos para Windows).
